meta_keywords: Yacht Services Nuku Hiva Marquesas French Polynesia
data.text:
We are your first point of contact on the island of Nuku-Hiva in the Marquises, French Polynesia. We are located on the small quay near the dinghy tie up. Look for the Yellow store front as you exit your dinghy.

Our mission is to help you enjoy your time in the Marquises to the fullest. We can provide almost anything you need or desire. From Mechanics to rental cars to tattoos WE CAN HELP.

Please view our services page for a compressive list of services we are prepared to provide. We are here to help!
